Sept 01. Add dependencies from:
                    https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/org.hibernate/hibernate-core/4.1.6.Final
                    https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/mysql/mysql-connector-java/5.1.38

Sept 02. Installing Hibernate Plugin in Eclipse :
                    MarketPlace -> search for Hibernate -> Choose Jboss & select hibarnate only


Sept 03. Configuring Hibernate in Eclipse :

                  File-> Others -> Hibernate Configaration File (cfg.xml)
